    <line rend="center"><milestone unit="tei:head" spanTo="#c57-0031.11"/><add hand="#pbs">another Chapter</add><anchor xml:id="c57-0031.11"/></line>
    <line>Sometime elapsed before I <mod spanTo="#c57-0031.01"/><del rend="strikethrough"
